To install the dependencies, please enter the following command while actively in the 'src' directory.

This software was designed for educational purposes, and I do not condone for it to be used maliciously. I also decline any responsibility for the misuse of this software. Any illegal or repercussive actions that are carried out must be entirely accounted for by the individual doing so.

[*] pip install -r requirements.txt --break-system-packages

Please ensure that you install all of the dependencies within the requirements.txt file for full functionality.

DO NOT run the installation process as root; otherwise you may face issues when executing from a non-sudo account.

Use the --break-system-packages flag if you are running Python in a protected environment.
